label("Cats",1.5C,C); label("Other Pets",2B,C); label("Dogs", 1.7A,A);[/asy]

solution:
Subtract the first equation from the second: \begin{align*}
(x+y)-(x-y) &= 12-6\\
2y &= 6\\
y &= \boxed{3}.
\end{align*}

